column5: Ugly drum is the ticket!  Nice work!
I just gained 5 lb's looking at your pictures. Man they look good.
Atta boy. I have a off set barrel smoker and did some on the weekend as well. Not 9 racks however
Nice I smoked a pork shoulder this weekend.  I'm lazy these days and use an electric.   Doesn't taste quite as good as coal but it's 1/10 the the work.
Cool, well not the snow part, but the ribs look delish!
